rwg mwrU, Gr 1 iv`c gurU Amrdws jI dI bwxI[
Akwl purK ie`k hY Aqy siqgurU dI ikrpw nwl imldw hY[
hy pRBU! (jdoN mYN Awqmk Afolqw ivc lIn rhWgw, qW) ij`Qy qUM mYnUM ibTweyNgw mYN auQy bYTw rhWgw, ijQy qUM mYnUM ByjyNgw mYN auQy jwvWgw (Bwv, mYN hr vyly qyrI rzw ivc rhWgw)[
hy suAwmI! swrI isRStI ivc mYnUM qUM hI iek pwiqSwh (id`syNgw, qyrI ivAwpkqw dy kwrn DrqI dy) swry hI QW mYnUM piv`qr jwpxgy ]1]
